Sadly to report, you know where they're going?

00:42:17.639 --> 00:42:21.039
They're going to a lot of the Catholic churches, Anglican churches.

00:42:21.039 --> 00:42:22.039
You just look it up.

00:42:22.039 --> 00:42:23.439
It's what's happening.

00:42:23.439 --> 00:42:24.559
You know why they're going there?

00:42:24.559 --> 00:42:29.999
Because they see an institution, quote unquote, that has lasted through the centuries.

00:42:29.999 --> 00:42:30.999
That's their reasoning.

00:42:30.999 --> 00:42:32.119
That's their logic.

00:42:32.119 --> 00:42:33.559
I've read extensively on it.

00:42:33.559 --> 00:42:35.599
I've seen many things about it.

00:42:35.599 --> 00:42:37.639
And I'm telling you, it's happening.

00:42:37.639 --> 00:42:39.479
We're seeing it.

00:42:39.479 --> 00:42:43.559
Can I tell you, they're not going to get truth there.

00:42:43.559 --> 00:42:47.759
They're not going to get truth there.

00:42:47.759 --> 00:42:49.639
But they're sick of it.

00:42:49.639 --> 00:42:53.279
They're sick of all the things that are taking place in our society today.

00:42:53.279 --> 00:42:54.279
You know what they're doing?

00:42:54.279 --> 00:42:55.279
They're looking.

00:42:55.279 --> 00:42:56.639
They're searching.

00:42:56.639 --> 00:42:57.959
They're seeking.

00:42:57.959 --> 00:43:02.679
Listen, we've got to be actively involved in influencing.

00:43:02.679 --> 00:43:09.239
Because I'm telling you, if you look at those denominations, if we can use that phrase,

00:43:09.239 --> 00:43:11.959
their attendance is going like this.

00:43:11.959 --> 00:43:13.319
They're seeing a spike.

00:43:13.319 --> 00:43:17.479
Listen, they're dusting out the pews that they haven't been dusting out in a long time.

00:43:17.479 --> 00:43:20.559
This is what they're saying.

00:43:20.559 --> 00:43:23.039
Because there's a generation that's sick of it.

00:43:23.039 --> 00:43:27.519
They've been lied to, and they've been lied to, and they've been lied to.

00:43:27.519 --> 00:43:29.959
We have the truth.

00:43:29.959 --> 00:43:33.239
We need to have this plea for influence.

00:43:33.239 --> 00:43:37.759
God, would you give me the opportunity to influence?

00:43:37.759 --> 00:43:40.559
To be actively engaged.

00:43:40.559 --> 00:43:41.999
To be present.

00:43:41.999 --> 00:43:43.599
To be purposed.

00:43:43.599 --> 00:43:46.639
God, would you give me a passion to influence?

00:43:46.639 --> 00:43:52.639
Would you help those that are observing me to know that I'm serious about the truth of

00:43:52.639 --> 00:43:54.639
your word, that I have a passion.

00:43:54.639 --> 00:43:57.919
We sing the song, a passion to reach the lost.

00:43:57.919 --> 00:44:00.999
Oh God, give us a passion.

00:44:00.999 --> 00:44:03.639
And then we see the purpose.

00:44:03.639 --> 00:44:04.639
How sad.

00:44:04.679 --> 00:44:10.799
I've had experiences where I've knocked on doors of individuals that are just a generation

00:44:10.799 --> 00:44:18.799
away from someone that was a Baptist deacon, a Baptist preacher, and you knock on their

00:44:18.799 --> 00:44:23.639
door and they have no clue about salvation, raising their kids, they don't even know anything

00:44:23.639 --> 00:44:25.639
about the Bible.

00:44:25.639 --> 00:44:29.639
You say, how does that happen?

00:44:29.639 --> 00:44:33.119
Somewhere along the line there was a lack of influence.

00:44:33.119 --> 00:44:35.439
Let me understand that every man has their own decision.

00:44:35.439 --> 00:44:37.919
Every man has their own choice.

00:44:37.919 --> 00:44:41.119
But I want you to understand that we need to be actively engaged.

00:44:41.119 --> 00:44:42.119
Let me ask this question.

00:44:42.119 --> 00:44:49.799
It's a question I've had a hard time getting away from in the last couple of weeks.

00:44:49.799 --> 00:45:01.719
How much would our children know to be true about God if we were their only instructor?

00:45:01.719 --> 00:45:11.999
How much would our children know to be true about God if we were their only instructor?

00:45:11.999 --> 00:45:16.299
Before God ever established the church, he established the home.

00:45:16.299 --> 00:45:18.319
The home does not replace the church.

00:45:18.319 --> 00:45:22.039
Excuse me, the church does not replace the home.

00:45:22.039 --> 00:45:28.839
The church is an institution that God has ordained and instructed and he's using.

00:45:28.839 --> 00:45:35.399
But the responsibility of training children has always been and will always be the responsibility

00:45:35.399 --> 00:45:38.959
of the parents.

00:45:38.959 --> 00:45:42.599
God established the home well before he established the church.

00:45:42.599 --> 00:45:50.399
The church comes alongside and aids in that instruction, in that bringing up.

00:45:50.399 --> 00:45:52.919
It's what the church does.

00:45:53.919 --> 00:46:00.319
Pastor, my kid's a mess, it must be your problem, it's not my problem.

00:46:00.319 --> 00:46:03.999
I'm just simply saying, no, no one said that to me, I'm just saying you read that kind

00:46:03.999 --> 00:46:04.999
of thing.

00:46:04.999 --> 00:46:11.159
What I'm saying is how much would our kids, how much would our kids know to be true about

00:46:11.159 --> 00:46:15.039
God if I were their only instructor?

00:46:15.039 --> 00:46:18.719
I'm thankful for the Sunday school teachers, I'm thankful for the junior church workers,

00:46:18.719 --> 00:46:25.999
I'm thankful for those that are actively engaged, church leaders, church members that

00:46:25.999 --> 00:46:28.599
are actively engaged in instructing.

00:46:28.599 --> 00:46:31.399
Praise God for that.

00:46:31.399 --> 00:46:36.999
But understand, the responsibility is ours.

00:46:36.999 --> 00:46:39.199
And it's a weighty responsibility.

00:46:39.199 --> 00:46:44.359
But God will help us and God will give us all that we need to fulfill what he's called

00:46:44.359 --> 00:46:45.359
us to fulfill.

00:46:45.759 --> 00:46:48.279
Oh, that God would help each of us this morning.

00:46:48.279 --> 00:46:53.839
Again, it's Father's Day, so some application of fathers, but we think about the truth broadly

00:46:53.839 --> 00:47:01.159
speaking that we as believers are to make known God's truth to a next generation.

00:47:01.159 --> 00:47:03.839
Oh, that God would give us a passion to do so.

00:47:03.839 --> 00:47:04.839
Let's pray together.

00:47:04.839 --> 00:47:07.839
Father, we do love you this morning.

00:47:07.839 --> 00:47:09.379
We thank you so much for loving us.

00:47:09.379 --> 00:47:13.479
We thank you for the word of God and for the truth that's contained therein.

00:47:14.199 --> 00:47:18.879
God, I pray that you would help us to be passionate about the truth of thy word.

00:47:18.879 --> 00:47:24.779
I pray that those that are observing our life and our behavior would know that there's nothing

00:47:24.779 --> 00:47:30.839
that even comes close to our passion.

00:47:30.839 --> 00:47:35.679
But this passion that we have for you and for your truth to make it known, God, help

00:47:35.679 --> 00:47:40.119
us to be engaged actively.

00:47:40.119 --> 00:47:43.039
I pray, Father, that you'd be with each one that's here this morning.

00:47:43.599 --> 00:47:48.599
I pray that you'd help us to recognize the opportunities that you've set before us.

00:47:48.599 --> 00:47:51.759
God, some of us have children.

00:47:51.759 --> 00:47:53.839
Some of us have grandchildren.

00:47:53.839 --> 00:48:00.079
Some of us, Lord, do not have children, but Lord, there's someone to influence.

00:48:00.079 --> 00:48:05.639
I pray that you'd help us to walk so close to thee, to be so filled with thy power and

00:48:05.639 --> 00:48:10.799
with thy spirit, to be so filled with your goodness and your greatness that we can't

00:48:10.799 --> 00:48:18.079
help but talk of all thy wondrous works to declare thy greatness to another generation.

00:48:18.079 --> 00:48:19.079
Help us, Lord.

00:48:19.079 --> 00:48:24.399
I pray that you'd move and work in the moments of invitation as only you can, and we'll thank

00:48:24.399 --> 00:48:25.399
you for every decision.

00:48:25.399 --> 00:48:27.519
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:48:27.519 --> 00:48:28.039
Would you stand with us?

